cat << EOF
A simple user-friendly interface to the php.ini
configuration file.
This is a GUI built in PHP-Gtk2. The various
configuration options are described in an XML
file which enables easy addition and editing of
the configuration options themselves.
* Can parse any existing INI file or generate
new ones.
* Preserves all existing comments if any
(normal and even inline).
* Can add comments from the GUI itself.
* Default values and description of each option
mentioned to aid configuration.
EOF

